structure.unit: RELIGIOUS, CHARITABLE, AND EDUCATIONAL SOCIETIES -- NONSTOCK, NONPROFIT CORPORATIONS

law.text: One (1) or more persons may act as the incorporator or incorporators of a corporation by delivering articles of incorporation to the Secretary of State for filing.
law.history: Amended 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 23, sec. 198, effective January 1, 1989. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 27, sec. 3. -- Created 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 165, sec. 27.
